blog.description: Yukalie, but you want to just call me Yuka for short. I am 16 and in Norway. I sometimes draw, and I write short fanfiction, mostly drabbles and shipping I am a multishipper for many fandoms. My ship list is here. You will see if I post artwork it is mostly DuckTales for the new and old show, Star Vs, Gravity Falls, Undertale, a lot of the assortment of things. You may message me for roleplay! Selection: Webby Vanderquack, Star Butterfly, May (Pokemon), Mimikyu, Glaceon.You can see my art tagged: MyArt.
